{"tid":60794,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］［暗黑料理］無骨仿蟹柳雞翼","createTime":"2016-12-30T17:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T11:01:49.000Z","uid":7033,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"629235203871e6cd0b9d96b4e2bbe700f06ad0ec","tid":60794,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"完sem太得閒無野做所以煮下野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n材料有:<br />\n雞翼<br />\n仿蟹柳<br />\n黑椒粉<br />\n鹽<br />\n<br />\n首先將雞翼去骨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/004907_7b6beb91a9a2931b90ab70630444e544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F004907_7b6beb91a9a2931b90ab70630444e544.jpg&h=d3f7c9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先斬開雞翼頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNQjdXS3679j9hYS6nvRkzqpZkBnRszim3TJ5EtrWtmuu?filename=10D3ZJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10D3ZJA.jpg&h=e64e00cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再用刀切分開兩條骨<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc31ipmp7shRhZx9PWrBEzzaioWaEwdedAnHy7T2AyhvS?filename=v9zmsP9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9zmsP9.jpg&h=676c2efd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/005051_9fb283c5aedadf2de9b1da387b5def96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F005051_9fb283c5aedadf2de9b1da387b5def96.jpg&h=f58b7b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就加鹽同黑椒粉醃一晚<br />\n<br />\n第二朝就可以加蟹柳入去啦!<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXt8dfhFAfzJcdnmb2sJHhhZoAbTtyiEw8QBA5HwVMKkK?filename=6634s02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6634s02.jpg&h=ae95ff0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隊條蟹柳入去嗰時好似灌腸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就可以炸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/005518_7f3758c5f1fe38dec447ad6cff6ba1f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F005518_7f3758c5f1fe38dec447ad6cff6ba1f3.jpg&h=71f43288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞翼面同底各炸5分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaFJL7FdbVxUPsjXMoQfntkZwtJZ1qGHkDYmzLNTZhhrq?filename=43Hz9HF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43Hz9HF.jpg&h=69cbf668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再每條邊炸2.5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n完成！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/005741_532c63b433a90558ef05c1eaa3b91d2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F005741_532c63b433a90558ef05c1eaa3b91d2c.jpg&h=ade4e4bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b33cf71afd97fe53c3b114ca7c35ce61a221f6f8","tid":60794,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"好撚正呀！屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f66494ec39a292017d3a5fd841199f9823fc99","tid":60794,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4948ad997cbbd4ba0b51c70f1455a3d94df6b397","tid":60794,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa8f3558bf29636ddea6e14f06b52fadd75959b","tid":60794,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好味呀，點沙律醬可能更加好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue